rComments: Made learning Japanese so much fun! Really amazing prof, but the once-a-class breakout rooms will kill your spirit if no one talks.

Sugimura sensei was always helpful and patient with us when we asked questions. Participation and attending lectures are 100% necessary when learning a new language, and if you dedicate yourself you'll see how passionate she is about teaching. It'll definitely be a memorable experience, and I enjoyed this class so much so I'm taking the next level!

She's really sweet and kind. I loved her class! If you have any questions she always happy to help. She's also really patient and caring. If you pay attention, do the exercises and study a little bit, you will do great in her class.
